{"title":"Template: DESCRIPTION","markdown":{"headingText":"Template: DESCRIPTION","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n```{text}\nPackage: cityOpenData\nType: Package\nTitle: A Lightweight Interface to CITY_NAME Open Data APIs\nVersion: 0.1.0\nAuthors@R:\n    person(\n      \"FIRST_NAME\", \"LAST_NAME\",\n      email = \"your.email@example.com\",\n      role = c(\"aut\", \"cre\"),\n      comment = c(\n        GitHub = \"YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME\",\n        ORCID = \"YOUR_ORCID\"\n      )\n    )\nDescription: Provides a unified set of helper functions to access datasets\n    from the CITY_NAME Open Data platform <https://SOCRATA_DOMAIN/>.\n    Functions return results as tidy tibbles and support optional filtering,\n    sorting, and row limits via the Socrata API. The package provides a\n    consistent interface for discovering and downloading datasets from the\n    CITY_NAME Open Data Portal using human-readable dataset keys or official\n    Socrata dataset identifiers.\nLicense: MIT + file LICENSE\nEncoding: UTF-8\nRoxygenNote: 7.3.3\nImports:\n    curl,\n    dplyr,\n    httr,\n    janitor,\n    jsonlite,\n    rlang,\n    tibble\nSuggests:\n    ggplot2,\n    knitr,\n    rmarkdown,\n    scales,\n    testthat (>= 3.0.0),\n    tidyr,\n    vcr (>= 0.6.0),\n    webmockr\nURL: https://YOUR_WEBSITE, https://github.com/YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME/cityOpenData\nBugReports: https://github.com/YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME/cityOpenData/issues\nVignetteBuilder: knitr\nConfig/testthat/edition: 3\nDepends:\n    R (>= 3.5)\n```\n\n## Checklist\n\n| Template value           | Replace with                            |\n|--------------------------|-----------------------------------------|\n| `cityOpenData`           | Your package name (e.g., `chiOpenData`) |\n| `CITY_NAME`              | Full city name                          |\n| `SOCRATA_DOMAIN`         | The city's Open Data portal domain      |\n| `FIRST_NAME`             | Your first name                         |\n| `LAST_NAME`              | Your last name                          |\n| `your.email@example.com` | Your email address                      |\n| `YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME`   | Your GitHub username                    |\n| `YOUR_ORCID`             | Your ORCID identifier (optional)        |\n| `https://YOUR_WEBSITE`   | Package website (pkgdown or other)      |\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"jupyter"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"notebook-links":true},"pandoc":{"standalone":true,"wrap":"none","default-image-extension":"png","to":"html","toc":true,"number-sections":true,"output-file":"template-description.html"},"language":{"toc-title-document":"Table of contents","toc-title-website":"On this page","related-formats-title":"Other Formats","related-notebooks-title":"Notebooks","source-notebooks-prefix":"Source","other-li